			Profile
			
			DongxiaoLIwasborninZhejiangprovince,P.R.China,in1976.HereceivedtheB.S.degreeinelectronicengineering,theM.S.degreeincommunicationandelectronicsystems,andthePh.D.degreeininformationandcommunicationengineering,allfromZhejiangUniversity,Hangzhou,P.R.China,in1997,2000,and2004,respectively.
&nbsp;
HeiscurrentlyanAssociateProfessorwiththeDepartmentofInformationScienceandElectronicEngineering,ZhejiangUniversity,andZhejiangProvincialKeyLaboratoryofInformationNetworkTechnology.HeisaseniormemberofChinaInstituteofCommunications,amemberofIEEESignalProcessingSocietyandComputerSociety.
&nbsp;
HeteachescoursesonDigitalImageProcessing,DataAnalysisandAlgorithmDesign,andRadioFrequencyCommunicationCircuits.HisresearchinterestsspantheareasofImageProcessing,ComputerVision,andMixedReality.HisresearchworkisdevotedtoThree-DimensionalTelevisioninrecentyears.HehasbeentheprincipalinvestigatorofseveralprojectsfundedbytheZhejiangProvincialNaturalScienceFoundationofChina,ScienceTechnologyDepartmentofZhejiangProvince,theNationalNaturalScienceFoundationofChina,andtheNationalScienceandTechnologyMajorProjectoftheMinistryofScienceandTechnologyofChina.Theresearchresultshavebeenpublishedinanumberofinternationaljournalsandconferenceproceedings,andgranted21inventionpatentsbytheStateIntellectualPropertyOfficeofP.R.China.
